title: Meet our CEO
description: Learn about what does it mean to join Strive School from Tobia, our CEO. You can ask anything about the program, pricing, schedule, career support and more. We'll help you learn if Strive School is the right choice for you.

title: Meet our Faculty
description: Meet our Faculty and ask all the questions you like about the program, the syllabus, the content, or the projects. How a day in Strive School looks like? What is the role of a Full Stack, AI or Frontend engineer looks like? Just join and ask about it!
